                            <comment id="16563545" author="paulk" created="Tue, 31 Jul 2018 12:08:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have made the change you suggested. It would be great if you can test out the snapshot release artifacts from e.g. the CI server.&lt;br/&gt;
